Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This strange story began{\i0}\N{\i1}on a blistering hot day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had received an unexpected mail{\i0}\N{\i1}from an old acquaintance of mine...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...but the message was just this:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Seek the sacred beast from Anzan."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I am at the meeting place{\i0}\N{\i1}of the four gods."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pao, the sender of the message,{\i0}\N{\i1}was an acquaintance of mine...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...but it didn't mean that we{\i0}\N{\i1}kept in touch all that well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I grew suspicious, and started{\i0}\N{\i1}to research Pao's current whereabouts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They say that Pao is one of the three{\i0}\N{\i1}greatest Feng Shui masters here on Mars.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But when I found his whereabouts,{\i0}\N{\i1}he had already left this world...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you weren't the\None that sent me this mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who visits from\Nthe inauspicious back door...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Receive the word from the heavens,\Nand lead me to the sun stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like what the pa-kua told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:02:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you shooting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure are disrespectful fellows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The escape route!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Escape route!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi of Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That was really close!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, over there... Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's a new girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,For that, she's rather young.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird one, hot dog bun, loved one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's his secret love-child?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,For that, she's rather old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Child, mild, wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't expecting Pao's daughter\Nto be this old already...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably don't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I met you once when\Nyou were this little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just an acquaintance.\NIt's been 10 years already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But your father sure was unlucky\Nto be in a traffic accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,On the way to Jupiter, there was a sudden\Nspatial fluctuation in hyperspace...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the "girlfriend?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.98,0:05:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the "secret love-child?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejected!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Jet, why were you at the graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody outside the family knows\Nhe got into an accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"Seek the sacred beast from Anzan."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"I am at the meeting place\Nof the four gods."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Pao sent me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right before the accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Can you help me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure this is the whereabouts\Nof the sun stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sun stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The direction, day, and time you arrived\Nwas the best combination for Feng Shui!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially when you're\Nsearching for something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It was?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It was!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Mr. Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. About that, we will have it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How was the boss feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way it could be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't have any particular favors{\i0}\N{\i1}to repay to Pao or this girl...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...but I decided to help them for now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There were too many things that made{\i0}\N{\i1}me suspicious to leave it alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did Pao send me mail{\i0}\N{\i1}right before his death?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do those words mean?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who were those guys that attacked us?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And there was something about{\i0}\N{\i1}this girl named Meifa as well...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This universe is made\Nof three different Chis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,One is the Chi of Heaven,\Nthe energy that comes from the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,One is the Chi of Earth, the energy\Nthat comes from a planet's surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.45,0:07:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And lastly Chi of Magnetism, the Chi\Nthat organisms like ourselves produce.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi from organisms?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:08:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The human body always\Nproduces a magnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That magnetic field and\Nthe magnetic field of the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...react to one another\Nto create energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Universal Feng Shui is the\Ntechnology that reads the energies...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...of nature such as this to\Nuse them in everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Universal Feng Shui...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the same thing\Nas fortunetelling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Other fortunetelling methods\Nonly predict or prognosticate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Universal Feng Shui has the\Npower to make the bad into the good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, if you were a Feng Shui\Nmaster as powerful as my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I just realized that I never spent\Ntime like this with my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me point out that\NI'm not that old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, I would be a boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait, that would be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,At least I can be an\Nelder brother or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,ICE cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Mr. Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that "Anzan" refers to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mountain Hotel Building...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiryu!\N(Blue Dragon)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Byakko!\N(White Tiger)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Genbu!\N(Black Turtle)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzaku!\N(Scarlet Phoenix)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, the cross-zenith method!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun stone is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are.\NThey're right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally found it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be the sun stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Jet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Outta the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,One bottle of lao-chu.\NI don't need a glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, you think we would\Ntell you that easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We're from the Blue Snake...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.78,0:11:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So you ARE from a syndicate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you following us around?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:12:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I couldn't tell you that\Neven if you killed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It was because we couldn't get Pao...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So they told us to get\Nthe recipient of his mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on the low end so we\Ndon't know any more than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My father... is alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pao's words showed where{\i0}\N{\i1}this stone was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does that mean Pao is{\i0}\N{\i1}still alive somewhere?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did he want me to find this{\i0}\N{\i1}stone and do something with it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It feels like I created more{\i0}\N{\i1}mysteries instead of solving them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For now, I decided to check out{\i0}\N{\i1}this stone, which was our only clue.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a piece of the moon from\Nthat Gate accident 50 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We Feng Shui masters\Ncall it the sun stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's absorbed the fluctuations\Nin time and space...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...and conceals a tremendous\Namount of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only think of it\Nas a plain old rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how much would it be if we sold it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.41,0:13:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys, if you're gonna\Nsmoke, go smoke outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You always smoke in here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm turning this into a\Nnonsmoking area starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now, you're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This ship is MY ship, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what are you gonna\Ndo with this stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I... have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:14:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what my\Nfather is thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ein! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The luopan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be...\NI took the magnet off...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... I get it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,THAT'S IT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly, my father\Nowned a sun stone as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that the two\Nstones are resonating...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...to show me the\Nwhereabouts of my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why Pao made you\Nlook for this stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.00,0:14:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why my father\Nsent the mail to you, Mr. Jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:15:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...and not to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They make a good couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dangerous combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The more righteous a guy\Nwas in his youth...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...the more likely he's gonna fall\Nfor a young girl later in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Really... Guys are so clueless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...was one that believed in Universal\NFeng Shui, but not other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So my mother left the house,\Nand took me along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That was seven years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure my father was able\Nto find our whereabouts easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But he never even tried\Nto look for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there was a reason behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was my father\Ntargeted by those men?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it because he was\Nfriends with bad people?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, tell me the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who my father really was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pao... was the consultant\Nfor a syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Pao had leaked\Ninformation to me about...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...the syndicate, back\Nwhen I was a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Pao already wanted out of\Nthe syndicate back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it's impossible\Nfor someone who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...important syndicate secrets\Nto ever leave the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Pao was afraid that more bad\Nthings would happen to his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure you can confirm\Nit all when you see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How about the radar?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No response.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be...\NI'm sure this is the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure are persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, Faye, please take care of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they YOUR guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me out if you don't\Nwanna die with this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.68,0:17:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What rotten luck of the draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sometimes it's good to act without{\i0}\N{\i1}asking "What's in it for me?".{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fairies who are going to\Ngrant the princess' wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Unmanned fighters?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.07,0:18:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So these would be the seven dwarves...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! They're trying to scare us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Spike! Come back here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apparently, if we apply lots{\i0}\N{\i1}of energy to that stone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...we can draw out all the{\i0}\N{\i1}forces trapped inside it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And, what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an all-or-nothing plan, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what it is, just hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:18:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I put it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Blast this rock with{\i0}\N{\i1}your plasma cannon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What a great plan this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looks like you made it in time, Jet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Pao! You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meifa... It's been a while.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Pao, you're in unstable territory.\NI can't approach any closer than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know... There isn't any{\i0}\N{\i1}oxygen left in here anyway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sent you that mail because I wanted{\i0}\N{\i1}you to bring my daughter here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... you willed us to be here\Nlike this using Feng Shui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:20:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true, Pao.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.91,0:21:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This wasn't your doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Meifa is here now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.33,0:21:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...because she WANTED to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You might be right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps I was being too hotheaded...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meifa... it's wonderful to{\i0}\N{\i1}see you one last time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.89,0:21:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I hated you all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I despised you all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.32,0:21:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.29,0:21:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, I don't know if it was a good thing{\i0}\N{\i1}or a bad thing that we took her along.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In any case, this was how{\i0}\N{\i1}this strange case ended.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She went back to Mars.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the smoking ban was lifted{\i0}\N{\i1}from the living quarters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once again, unchanging daily life{\i0}\N{\i1}has returned, just as it was before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.28,0:22:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One thing that has changed, though...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.16,0:22:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I no longer read the{\i0}\N{\i1}fortunetelling pages in magazines.{\i0}
