Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.36,0:24:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A man, Andy, made a sudden\Nappearance on horseback.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.53,0:24:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who in the world is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.28,0:24:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he an ally or a foe?\NOr is he a true cowboy?
